Class MIDITrackBuilder

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.rockhoppertech.music.midi.js.MIDITrackBuilder

  • public class MIDITrackBuilder
extends Object
    Decided in this case to not make it a static inner class. MIDITrack x = new MIDITrackBuilder().name("test").description("thing").build(); or MIDITrack x = new MIDITrack.Builder().name("test").noteString("C D E").build();
    Author:
    Gene De Lisa
